## Layout e Espacamento

- **Grid**: Bootstrap 5 (container, row, col-*) — no Tailwind, usar equivalentes (`container`, `grid`, `grid-cols-*`)
- **Max-width container**: 1320px
- **Section padding**: 4rem (mobile) → 5rem (desktop 1024px+) → 6rem (wide 1366px+)
- **Hero split**: col-lg-7 (texto) + col-lg-5 (visual)
- **Blog grid**: 3 colunas desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile

## Motion e Interacao

- **Card hover**: `transform: scale(1.15)` + `box-shadow: 0px 6px 6px 0px rgba(0,30,39,.1), 0px 16px 24px rgba(0,30,39,.15)`
- **Button hover**: `box-shadow: 0px 6px 0px 0px <cor-com-opacidade>`
- **Transicoes globais**: `all .2s linear`
- **Animacoes**: pulse (FAB), showUp (nav sticky), spinner (loading), animaDropLeft (dropdown)

## Componentes de Referencia

- **Search (Blog)**: input bg petroleo + btn verde lima, border-radius 20px
- **Accordion (FAQ)**: Bootstrap accordion padrao com estilos OMIE
- **Blog Card**: imagem + categoria (border-left 3px `#6EC1E4`) + data + titulo
- **Card Beneficio**: icone SVG + titulo + descricao, hover scale
- **Card Carousel Banner**: bg cinza, border 1px `#dbdfde`, border-radius 8px

## Icones

- SVGs inline (sem biblioteca externa)
- Tamanhos: 16px, 24px, 32px, 48px
- Cor herda do contexto (fill: currentColor ou explicito)

